latestPosts.caption:
🧿Emerging Couple Content Creators 2024 🧿
Last night was surreal! We were thrilled to receive our very FIRST award and we’re still pinching ourselves 🏆

What started as fun banter, random reels, and 'let’s-see-what-happens' moments turned into something that resonates with all of you. From laughter to lessons, your love and encouragement brought us here 💕

This isn’t just our award—it’s for every double tap, every share, every laugh you’ve shared with us. Thank you for being part of our journey 🫂

Thank you @maacindiaofficial for honouring us with the award 🙌🏻 and a special love-filled shoutout to @cloutpocketaces for helping us shine brighter every day. Here’s to more love, laughter, and stories together ❤️
